arStrings.szText:
Forged in Hall of the Penitent within central Dry Steppes to summon a powerful enemy. Requires {c_number}2{/c} in World Tier 3 and {c_number}5{/c} in World Tier 4. Found in Helltides from Tortured Gift of Living Steel.

Drops randomly from Elites, Local Events, Treasure Goblins, Whisper Caches, Hellborne, and Blood Maiden.
